# Vamstar — Healthcare Supply Analytics Case Study

## Company
Vamstar is a UK-based healthtech startup that connects hospitals 
with medical suppliers using AI-driven procurement analytics.

## Problem I Identified
Healthcare suppliers list the same product under different names 
across ERP systems. This causes duplicate orders, price mismatches, 
and wasted procurement budget.

## What I Built
A Power BI dashboard with:
- 5 KPI cards: Total Orders, Suppliers, Supply Value, 
  Avg Quality Score, Delayed Orders
- Duplicate product flag — automatically catches same products 
  listed under different names
- Supplier performance bar chart with colour coding
- Delivery status slicer for real-time filtering

## Tools Used
Power BI | DAX | Excel | Power Query

## Key Insights
- CarePlus BV has the highest delayed delivery rate
- PharmaSource India handles highest supply value (1.9K)
- 100% of products had duplicate naming issues — 
  confirming the core procurement data problem

